The paper proposes a method for continual learning in neural networks, which is a topic that falls under the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), neural networks (cs.NE), and natural language processing (cs.CL). However, since the paper focuses on image classification tasks and uses convolutional neural networks, it is most likely to belong to the cs.CV sub-category. The other sub-categories are also relevant since the paper discusses machine learning techniques, neural networks, and their applications in artificial intelligence.
